This module provides an interface to the Hunspell hyphenator (derived from 
libhnj). This hyphenator uses modified TeX hyphenation dictionaries. For 
details, see the hyphen-* directory.

Use:

> object h = Public.Tools.Language.Hyphenate("hyphen-2.8.6/hyph_en_US.dic"); 
> h->hyphenate("longfellow");                             
(1) Result: "longfel-low"
